messages.messageBody:
Ya, they appealed to me too LOL :O)))))

But I was 15 1/2 yo!!! And male!

:O))

Actually Spidey of the 70's was my fav super hero - he had troubles too, even with the powers I craved!
----- Original Message -----
From: starsuncloud@...
To: Unschooling-dotcom@yahoogroups.com
Sent: Friday, June 06, 2003 4:45 PM
Subject: [Unschooling-dotcom] Wishcraft


In a message dated 6/6/2003 5:25:19 PM Central Daylight Time,
Unschooling-dotcom@yahoogroups.com writes:
>
> I loved Wonder Woman too. I think I was her for Halloween at least 3 times.

Oh good, another Wonder Woman idol worshipper!! :)
I used to "fly" around my Grandmothers house with a red cape (usually a
blanket tied on) and tall boots if I could find some. What fun! I loved Charlie's
Angels too...any woman that could kick some A** really appealed to me.

Ren
